### GeoRide Backend API Testing

### =====================================

### 1️⃣ Get Nearby Drivers (Run multiple times to observe real-time updates)

GET http://localhost:5000/rider/nearby-drivers?lat=28.6140&lng=77.2091

### =====================================

### 2️⃣ Request Ride (Assign nearest driver)

POST http://localhost:5000/ride/request
Content-Type: application/json

{
"lat": 28.6140,
"lng": 77.2091
}

### =====================================

### 3️⃣ Verify After Assignment (Driver should now be BUSY)

GET http://localhost:5000/rider/nearby-drivers?lat=28.6140&lng=77.2091


